{
  "stem": "7777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told me, if you will take a job-- all the jobs was government jobs-- if you will take a job, you will stay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- they will not bother you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I went and I took a job in a factory from they make furniture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We work over there a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We get-- every day, we get 700 crumb of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They give us just bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, only we lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have-- I still have some little bit money with the friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later in this job, I changed to go to work in a factory was to make the board, to lumbers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The lumber.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We work over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Worked and worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, later, they said, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the 21st of-- this was the 21st of July-- the 22nd of July 1941.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was when the-- the war broke out is we saw the Russian start to send military.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Russian train was not mixing with the Polish train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They have wider tracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Is the all soldiers, where they come in from the Russia to go fight the German, they come into [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Zdolbunov ?] This was about eight mile from Kostopol.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we saw they send so much military.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Eight days, the military was going to the border to fight the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, this was-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] it was day and night they was going.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was not taking too long, maybe about two, three days later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they start to go back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's a day and a half they went, and this was all the soldiers where they went over there in eight days.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
